Privacy Policy for GenZ Cleaner

Effective Date: 14-09-2025

GenZ Cleaner (“we,” “our,” or “the App”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your information when using the GenZ Cleaner app.

1. Information We Collect

GenZ Cleaner is designed to clean and optimize your Android device. The App does not collect personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, email address, or location.

However, for the functionality of the App, we may access or process:

Device storage information (to identify junk files, cache, duplicate files, large files, and empty folders)

App usage information (to manage apps installed on your device)

All data is processed locally on your device. We do not upload, store, or share this data with any third party.

2. Use of Information

The information accessed by GenZ Cleaner is solely used to:

Identify and remove junk files, cache, and unnecessary data

Optimize device storage and performance

Provide features such as WhatsApp cleaning, image optimization, clipboard cleaning, and duplicate file detection

No personal data is used for advertising, analytics, or marketing purposes.

3. Advertising and Third-Party Services

GenZ Cleaner may display ads provided by third-party ad networks such as Google AdMob.

These ad networks may collect limited non-personal information such as device type, app usage statistics, or advertising identifiers to serve relevant ads.

We do not share any personal data with advertisers.

4. Permissions

To function correctly, GenZ Cleaner may request access to:

Storage (read/write) — to identify and clean unnecessary files

Installed apps — to manage or clean apps

All permissions are required only for app functionality and are processed locally on your device.

5. Data Security

We implement appropriate measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Since the App processes data locally, there is minimal risk of data being transmitted externally.

6. Children’s Privacy

GenZ Cleaner is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the App and the Play Store listing. Please review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: nexuswhitehat@gmail.com
